<p id="slogan">2013 IEEE International Conference on Service Operations and Logistics, and Informatics<br />July 28-30, 2013, Dongguan, Guangdong, China<br />Sponsored by IEEE/ITSS, Technical-sponsored by INFORMS<br /></p>
